*Lepo* jutro! (Good morning!)
Ona je *lepa*. (She is beautiful.)
Neka bude *lepo*. (Let it be nice.)
*Lepo* je bilo u parku. (It was nice in the park.)
*Lepše* je za njega. (It's better for him.)
To je *lepo* urađeno. (That is nicely done.)
Ona je *lepša* od njega. (She is prettier than him.)
Sutra ćemo biti *lepo* obučeni. (Tomorrow we will be nicely dressed.)
Ona traži *lepu* osobu. (She's looking for a nice person.)